As a teacher, I want to be able to create a profile with my name, subject, and grade level so that I can be easily matched to a qualified teaching assistant.

As a teacher, I want to be able to upload student work, so that it can be graded by a teaching assistant.

As a teacher, I want to be able to search for teaching assistants by subject, grade level, availablility, and rating, so that I can find a qualified TA to grade my students' work.

As a teacher, I want to be able to read reviews of teaching assistants, so that I know that they are reliable and can do good work.

As a teacher, I want to be able to rate teaching assistants that I have worked with, so that I can tell others my opinion on their quality of work. 

As a teacher, I want to be able to download graded student work, so that I can distribute it back to my students.

As a teaching assistant, I want to be able to create a profile with my name, experience, and subject and grade level preferences, so that I can be easily matched to a teacher.

As a teaching assistant, I want to be able to search for available assignments based on due dates, subject, and grade level, so that I can find assignments to grade.

As a teaching assistant, I want to be able to view student work, grade student work, give feedback, and enter grades, so that I can help teachers grade student work.

As a teaching assistant, I want to be able to message the teacher, so that I can ask any questions during the grading process. 